===== BEGIN FILE: .gitattributes =====
```
# Auto line ending normalization
* text=auto

# Binary files
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.gif binary
*.zip binary
*.jar binary
*.aar binary

# Keep line endings for scripts
*.sh text eol=lf
*.bash text eol=lf
gradlew text eol=lf

# Source files (consistent line endings)
*.ts text eol=lf
*.tsx text eol=lf
*.js text eol=lf
*.json text eol=lf
*.md text eol=lf